{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-clarify-information-in-different-interactions/task-84","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-how-to-clarify-information-in-different-interactions","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Slušaj, Marija, i odgovori na pitanje.</p>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"English","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-clarify-information-in-different-interactions/task-84"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Šta možemo reći o količini vegetarijskih jela/povrća na proslavi?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p>Maria veruje da bi trebalo da bude pet tanjira salate za proslavu</p>","feedback":"<p>Zapravo kaže da će biti dovoljno tri tanjirića.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Misli da su tri tanjira salate ono što je potrebno ljudima iz grupe povrća.</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Ataita, pet tanjira za salatu, zajedno sa tih 3 koja su se dogovorila da naruče</p>","feedback":"<p>To bi bilo previše, jer misli da će tri tanjiri biti dovoljno.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Želi da naruči tri tanjira za pileća krila jer misli da će biti dovoljno</p>","feedback":"<p>Pileća krilca su već bila pomenuta. Razgovor je sada o salati.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":2}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-boardroom.png","characters":[{"character":"Maria","position":{"x":50,"y":0,"z":1.5},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"4.3-5.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":26.62,"finishTimestamp":32.88},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Maria","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Maria","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":7.26,"dialogue":{"text":"And for the vegetarian